column3: New York Sṳ fe̍t-chá ham-cho Néu-yok-sṳ, he Mî-koet ngìn-khiéu chui-tô ke sàng-sṳ, ya-he chhiòn sṳ-kie chui-thai ke Tû-fi-khî chṳ̂-yit ——New York Tû-fi-khî ke fu̍t-sîm.
Philadelphia vì Mî-koet thi-ńg thai sàng, pin-chhiâ he Pennsylvania ngìn-khiéu chui-tô, mien-chit chui-thai ke sàng-sṳ.
Pâ-sî he Nàm Mî-chû yit-ke koet-kâ.
Québec-sén he Kâ-nâ-thai tûng-phu ke yit-ke sén.
Kalimantan he Yin-nì Borneo tó-song nàm-phu ke thi-fông.
Tô-lùn-tô he Kâ-nâ-thai Ontario-sén ke sú-fú, chhô-lo̍k chhai Ontario-fù sî-pet ngan ke Nàm Ontario thi-khî.

L'Aquila he yit-chho Yi-thai-li chûng-phu sàng-sṳ, Abruzzo fò L'Aquila-sén Sú-fú, ngìn-khiéu 72,913 ngìn, than-he kâ-sông mî-thiên chhai kin-nui chhiu thu̍k, chhiu ngia̍p fò lî-yû chá, ngìn-sú tha̍t-to 10 van.
Venezia he Yi-thai-li tûng-pet-phu chho̍k-miàng ke lî-yû lâu kûng-ngia̍p sàng-sṳ, ya-he Veneto thi-khî ke Sú-fú.
Piemonte he Yi-thai-li sî-pet ke yit-ke Thai-khî.
Pretoria he vi-yî Gauteng-sén pet-phu ke sàng-sṳ, he Nàm-fî ke hàng-chṳn sú-tû.
Cape Town he Nàm-fî ngìn-khiéu phài-miàng thi-ngi thai sàng-sṳ, ya-he Cape Town tû-fi sang-khî chû-sṳ̀n phu-fun, Sî Khôi-phú-sén sén-fi, Cape Town vi Nàm-fî li̍p-fap sú-tû.
Texas he Mî-koet ke yit-ke chû.

Den Haag he Hò-làn thi-sâm thai sàng-sṳ, chhai Â-mê-sṳ̂-thi̍t-tan lâu Lu̍k-thi̍t-tan chṳ̂ heu, ngìn-khiéu 510,909-ngìn, Thai Hói-ngà Thi-khî ngìn-khiéu yok 1,054,793-ngìn, mien-chit yok 100 phìn-fông kûng-lî.
Koet-kâ he chṳ́ yúng-yû khiung-thùng ke ngî-ngièn, vùn-fa, chúng-chhu̍k, hiet-thúng, liâng-thú, chṳn-khièn fe̍t-chá Li̍t-sṳ́ ke sa-fi khiùn-thí.
Sén he yit-ke hàng-chṳn-khî kip-phe̍t, ya-he Chûng-fà Mìn-koet lâu Chûng-fà Ngìn-mìn Khiung-fò-koet ke Yit-kip Hàng-chṳn-khî.
Chṳ́-set he yit-chúng yù séu-liòng fùng-set lâu làm-set fun-ha̍p tet-chhut ke ngân-set.
Chat-ho̍k Pok-sṳ, kô-kip ho̍k-hâm chṳ̂-yit, thûng-sòng he ho̍k-li̍t ka-kèu chûng chui kô-kip ke ho̍k-hâm.
Fôi-set he yit-chúng ngân-set.
Liá-piên "Chûng-kau" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"宗教" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Liá-piên "Ngân-set" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"顏色" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Ôn-sit-ngit-fi he Kî-tuk Sîn-kau ke yit-ke kau-phai, sṳ̀n-li̍p yî 1863-ngièn.
Chûng-set he yit-chúng yù fun-ha̍p séu-liòng fùng-set lâu liu̍k-set, chhâng-set lâu làm-set, fe̍t-chá vòng-set lâu chṳ́-set ngân-liau-é kèu-sṳ̀n ke ngân-set.
Koet-nui Sên-sán Chúng-chhṳ̍t he yit-thin sṳ̀-khì nui, yit-ke khî-vet nui ke kîn-chi fa̍t-thung chûng só sên-sán chhut chṳ̂ chhiòn-phu chui-chûng sṳ̀n-kó ke sṳ-chhòng ka-chhṳ̍t.
pH he yùng-yi̍t chûng Khîn lì-chṳ́ fa̍t-thu ke yit-chúng phêu-thu, ya chhiu-he thûng-sòng yi-ngi song yùng-yi̍t sôn-kán chhàng-thu ke fên-liòng phêu-chún.

Lu-tet kau-phai / Sin-ngi-chûng, fe̍t chhṳ̂n Lu-tet-chûng, vì Sîn-kau chûng-phai chṳ̂-yit, ngièn chhṳ 16 Sṳ-ki Tet-koet sṳ̀n ho̍k-kâ Mâ-tên Lu-tet vì kiet-sîn Thiên-chú-kau fi fat-hí ke chûng-kau kói-kiet yun-thûng, khì sṳ̀n ho̍k sṳ̂-sióng sṳ̀n-vì kói-kiet yun-thûng ke siong-chṳ̂n.
Làm-set he yit-tsúng set-tshái, têu-he fùng-liu̍k-làm kông ke sâm ngièn-set chûng ke yit-ngièn, tshai-yî liá sâm-tsúng ngièn-set chûng têu-ke pô-tshòng chui-tón, thai-yok si-pak tshit-sṳ̍p na̍p-mí.
Chóng-ló Kau-fi he Kî-tuk-kau Sîn-kau ke yit-phai, kîn-ngièn he chhiùng Sṳ̍p-liuk Sṳ-ki ke sî Êu-chû kói-kiet yun-thung khôi-sṳ́.
Liá-piên "Yî-sṳ̂-làn-kau" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"伊斯蘭教" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Liá-piên "Yù-thai-kau" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"猶太教" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Ńg-sùn-chiet Yun-thung he Ngi-sṳ̍p Sṳ-ki chhut-thèu hîn-hí ke Kî-tuk Sîn-kau chhai-nui ke yun-thung.

Vòng-set ke kông-pô tshòng-kie 565－590 mì-mí, fùng-set, liu̍k-set kông fun-ha̍p khó-yî sán-sên vòng-kông.
Sùn-tho-chûng fe̍t-chá Ví-lî-chûng he Kî-tuk-kau Sîn-kau chú-yeu chûng-phai chṳ̂-yit.

Liá-piên "Sîn-kau" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"新教" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.

column3: Mî-li-kiên Ha̍p-chung-koet Chhâm-ngi-yèn he Mî-koet ke li̍p-fap kî-kèu ──Mî-koet Koet-fi ke lióng-yen chṳ̂ yit, nang yit yen vì Chung-ngi-yèn.
Chhòn-ngiam-phiang he yit-chúng khó-yî chhiùng yit-ke ngìn fe̍t-chá khì-thâ vu̍t-chúng, kîn-ko kok-chúng thù-kang chhòn-ngiam pûn nang-ngoi yit-ke ngìn fe̍t vu̍t-chúng ke chhòn-ngiam-chṳn.
Chat-ho̍k Pok-sṳ, kô-kip ho̍k-hâm chṳ̂-yit, thûng-sòng he ho̍k-li̍t ka-kèu chûng chui kô-kip ke ho̍k-hâm.
Khien-không he chṳ́ sâng-vu̍t chhai chṳn-sòng ke sên-lî lâu sîm-lî chhong-khóng, mò ngim-hò phiang-thung.
Kám-mo, ya cho-tet ham-cho fûng-sià, fûng-hòn, he sông-fû-khi̍p-tho su phiang-thu̍k kám-ngiam yín-hí ke yit chúng chhòn-ngiam-phiang.
Soi-muk he thung-vu̍t ke yit chúng sâng-lî hien-siong.
Thung-fûng he yit-chúng yîn-phiau lèn thoi chhia chong-ngai, sṳ́ ngiau sôn lùi-chit yì yín-hí ke chhi̍t-phiang, su̍k-yî Kôan-chiet yàm ke yit-chúng, yu chhṳ̂n thoi chhia sin Kôan-chiet yàm.
Chhú-yi̍t he yîn-vi chhú-yi̍t-khiùn yín-hí ke chhòn-ngiam-phiang.

Ên-tién tshai Kî-tuk-kau chûng he Song-ti tui ngìn-lui yit-tsúng tsûng-tsú ke péu-hien, thi̍t-phe̍t he yû-kûan kiu-su̍k fông-mien, lâu sṳ̍t-tsṳt hàng-thung fe̍t hàng-vì, yàng-tet ke ka-tshṳ̍t fe̍t-tsá pûn tsṳn-mìn ke san-liòng mò-kûan.
Pot-sâ he yit-chúng phiang.
Liù-hàng-sin kám-mo, kién-chhṳ̂n liù-kám, he yit chúng yîn-vi liù-kám phiang-thu̍k yín-hí ke chhòn-ngiam-phiang.
Kyril Sṳ-mû he thûng-hàng yî Slav Ngî-chhu̍k thai-tô-su mìn-chhu̍k chûng ke sṳ-mû sû-siá ne-thúng.
Phiang ya ham-cho chhi̍t-phiang, he sâng-vu̍t chhai yit-thin ngièn-yîn ke sún-hoi-sin chok-yung hâ, yîn chhṳ-vún thiàu-chiet fún-lon yì fat-sâng ke yi-sòng sâng-miang fa̍t-thûng ko-chhàng.
Het-sí-phiang, ya cho-tet ham-cho het-vûn-yi̍t, he ngìn-lui li̍t-sṳ́ sông chui ngiàm-chhûng ke vûn-yi̍t chṳ̂-yit.
Pot-thâm-fó he sòng-kien pin khó chṳ-miang ke yit-chúng chhòn-ngiam-phiang, yù Fûn-kî-hon-khiûn thô-chṳ.

Kôan-chiet-yàm he chhiòn-sṳ-kie chui sòng-kien ke man-sin chhi̍t-phiang, chṳ́ -yeu he Kôan-chiet ke ngiôn-kut thui-fa fe̍t-chá Kiet-thì chû-chṳt fat-yàm, thô-chṳ Kôan-chiet thung-thung chhiùng yì kòn yéu Kôan-chiet ke chang-sòng yun-thûng chhiu kiàu Kôan-chiet yàm, chúng-khiung yû Yit-pak tô-ke chúng-lui.
Kôn-yàm he Kôn-chhóng yîn phiang-thu̍k, yo̍k-vu̍t, chiú-chîn fe̍t-chá thoi-chhia yi-sòng yîn-hí ke fat-yàm chṳn-chhong.
Chho̍k-thiên-tiau he ngìn ke làn-mî yit-chúng phiang.
Pha̍k-hèu he yit-chúng yù pha̍k-hèu kòn-khiûn yín-hí ke kip-sin fû-khi̍p tho-chhòn ngiam-phiang, tô-kien yî chhiû Tûng-kui.
A-hîn Kôn-yàm, Thai-liu̍k, Hiông-kóng, Àu-mùn, Mâ-Sîn yi̍t chok Kap-hîn-kôn-yàm, chhai Chûng-koet Thai-liu̍k sòng kién-chhṳ̂n A-kôn.
Pông-hâ he yit-chúng sòng-kien ke hì-tho ke man-sin yàm-tsin-sin chhi̍t-phiang, chú-yeu thi̍t-chṳ̂n he tô-pien lâu fu̍k-fat ke tsin-chhong, khó-ngia̍k-sin hì-liù chú-set.

Ngìn-khiéu thûng-sòng he chṳ́ yit-ke thi-lî khî-vet ngìn ke su-muk, tui ngìn-khiéu chin-hàng ngiên-kiu ke khô-muk yû Sa-fi-ho̍k lâu Thi-lî-ho̍k, kì he ngìn-khiéu ngiên-kiu ke chui kî-pún ke fam-vì, yit-ke thi-vet ke sṳ̀n-chai nèn-li̍t he yû-han ke, liá han-chṳ ngìn-khiéu su-muk ke chen-chóng.
Mî-li-kiên Ha̍p-chung-koet Hièn-fap kién-chhṳ̂n Mî-koet Hièn-fap, he Mî-koet ke kîn-pún thai-fap, thièn-thin Mî-koet chṳn-chhṳ chṳ-thu ke fap-li̍t kî-chhú.
Het-sí-phiang, ya cho-tet ham-cho het-vûn-yi̍t, he ngìn-lui li̍t-sṳ́ sông chui ngiàm-chhûng ke vûn-yi̍t chṳ̂-yit.
Thiap-sú-chang he ke-ngìn li-yung chṳt-vu ke phien-li, kiám ngìn ke chhòi-vu̍t, vì phe̍t-ngìn chhí li-yit ke hàng-vì.

Machiavelli he Yi-thai-li ke chṳn-chhṳ-chat-ho̍k-kâ,yîm-ngo̍k-kâ,sṳ̂-ngìn fò long-man-chú-yi hi-ki-kâ.Kì he Yi-thai-li vùn-ngi-fu̍k-hîn ke thoi-péu ngìn-vu̍t.Kì siá ke Kiûn-chú-lun he hien-sṳ̍t-chú-yi chṳn-chhṳ lî-lun ke khôi-tôn,yì lun-Livius chet thì-chhong khiung-fò-chú-yi.
George 3-sṳ, 1760-ngièn 10-ngie̍t 25-ngit tên-kî cho Thai Britain khi̍p Ireland koet-vòng.

George 4-sṳ, chhiòn-miàng George Augustus Frederick, Yîn-koet Fòng-sṳt sṳ̀n-yèn, 1762-ngièn chṳ 1820-ngièn yî vòng-tú sṳ̂n-fun chhut-ngim Wales Chhîn-vòng, 1811-ngièn chṳ 1820-ngièn khì-kiên yîn-vì fu vòng George 3-sṳ fam chîn-sṳ̀n phiang yì kiâm ngim ngiap chṳn vòng, 1820-ngièn 1-ngie̍t 29-ngit chang-sṳt ki-sṳ̀n fu vòng chhut-ngim thai Britain lâu Ireland lièn-ha̍p Vòng-koet lièn-ha̍p Vòng-koet koet-vòng lâu Hannover Vòng-koet koet-vòng, chṳ 1830-ngièn 6-ngie̍t 26-ngit kàm-pen.
Ludwig van Beethoven he yit-chak si̍p kú-tién chú-ngi thai-sṳ̀n, khôi long-man chú-ngi siên-hò ke Tet-koet chok-khiuk-kâ, ya-he yên-cheu-kâ thùng chṳ́-fî-kâ.
Victor Hugo he Fap-koet ke yit chak long-man chú-ngi chok-kâ.

Frédéric Chopin, he Pô-làn Chok-khiuk-kâ lâu Kong-khìm-kâ, kì he li̍t-sṳ́ sông chui khí yáng-hióng-li̍t lâu chui su fôn-ngiàng ke kòng-khìm Chok-khiuk-kâ chṳ̂-yit, he Pô-làn yîm-ngo̍k sṳ́-sông chui chhùng-yeu ke ngìn-vu̍t chṳ̂-yit, he Êu-chû 19 Sṳ-ki Long-màn Chú-ngi yîm-ngo̍k ke thoi-péu ngìn-vu̍t.
Pâ-sṳ-tet he Fap-kok mì-sâng-vu̍t-ho̍k-kâ, fa-ho̍k-kâ, mì-sâng-vu̍t-ho̍k ke chhóng-li̍p-chak chi-yit.
Edward 7-sṳ, chhiòn-miàng Albert Edward, Yîn-koet koet-vòng, Yin-thu Fòng-ti.
Alexander Graham Bell he Kâ-nâ-thai ke yit chak khô-ho̍k-kâ.
George 5-sṳ, chhiòn-miàng George Frederick Ernest Albert, Edward 7-sṳ lâu Alexandra fòng-heu ke chhṳ chṳ́.
Adolf Hitler he Nazi Tet-koet chhai 1933-ngièn chṳ 1945-ngièn khì-kiên ke chui kô liâng-thô-ngìn.

Edward 8-sṳ, Yîn-koet koet-vòng, chhiòn-miàng Edward Albert Christian George Andrew Patrick David, sùn-vi heu pûn khì thi George 6-sṳ fûng vì vûn sâ kûng tsiok, chhṳ 1936-ngièn 1-ngie̍t 20-ngit khì fu George 5-sṳ kàm pen to 1936-ngièn 12-ngie̍t 11-ngit thui vi, vì Yîn-koet fò Yîn Lièn-pâng kok-chhṳ-chhṳ liâng koet-vòng, Yin-thu Fòng-ti, khiung chhai-vi 325 thiên.
George 6-sṳ, ngièn-miàng Albert Frederick Arthur George, Yîn-koet koet-vòng khi̍p chung chhṳ-chhṳ liâng koet-vòng, 1936-ngièn 12-ngie̍t 11-ngit chṳ 1952-ngièn 2-ngie̍t 6-ngit chhai-vi.
Liá-piên "Alexandros Thai-ti" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"亞歷山大大帝" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Muhammad he Yî-sṳ̂-làn-kau ke yit ke siên-tî.
Vì-kit-ngì he Lò-mâ chui ví-thai ke kú-tién sṳ̂-ngìn.
Â-ha̍p-vòng (Hî-pak-lói-vùn:אַחְאָב‎, ？

Ngâ-li-ôn-ngìn, chhai tông-kîm ke ho̍k-su̍t kie, liá-ke su̍t-ngî chhai thai-tô-sú chhìn-khóng hâ yí pûn chhí-thoi vì "Yin-thu Yî-lóng-ngìn" fe̍t "Yin-Êu-ngìn", chit kóng "Yin-thu Yî-lóng Ngî-chhu̍k" fe̍t Yin-Êu Ngî-ne ngî-ngièn ke ngìn. "Ngâ-li-ôn" hien chhai kífû yung-yî ngî-ngièn ho̍k-su̍t ngî Yin-thu Ngâ-li-ôn Ngî-kî chûng, "Ngâ-li-ôn-ngìn" chhiu-he kóng liá-chak ngî-kî ke ngî-ngièn ke ngìn.
Thiên-fòng he Ngi̍t-pún ke kiûn-chú.
Kôn-yîm, Kôn-sṳ-yîm, Kôn-sṳ-yîm phù-sat, tang tang hai Fut-kaau yit ko phù-sat.
Leonardo da Vinci he Êu-chû Vùn-ngi fu̍k-hîn sṳ̀-khì Yi-thai-li ke yit ke chhut-miàng ke fa-kâ.

William Shakespeare phî hó-tô ngìn ngin-vì he Yîn-koet vùn-ho̍k-sṳ́ lâu hi-ki-sṳ́ song chui ví-thai ke sṳ̂-ngìn lâu ki-chok-kâ, ya he sî-fông vùn-ngi-sṳ́ song chui khiet-chhut ke chok-kâ chṳ̂-yit, chhiòn sṳ-kie chok-yê ke ki-chok-kâ chṳ̂-yit.
Gottfried Leibniz, Tet-yi-chṳ Chet-ho̍k-kâ, Sú-ho̍k-kâ.
Abraham Lincoln, Mî-koet tsṳn-tshṳ-kâ, thi sṳ̍p-liuk ngim tsúng-thúng, ya-he sú-vi Khiung-fò-tóng si̍t tsúng-thúng.
Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart he yit-chak si̍p kú-tién chú-ngi thai-sṳ̀n, khôi long-man chú-ngi siên-hò ke O-thi-li chok-khiuk-kâ, ya-he yên-cheu-kâ thùng chṳ́-fî-kâ.

column2: ['nâ-pho-lùn yit-sṳ', 'napoleon 1-sṳ', '拿破侖一世', '拿破崙一世']
column3: Napoleon yit-sṳ he Fap-koet chṳn-chhṳ lâu kiûn-sṳ liâng-siu, Kî tui 19 sṳ-ki vân-khí ke êu-chû chṳn-chhṳ yáng-hióng hàn-thai.
Elizabeth 2-sṳ he Yîn-koet ńg-vòng, Yîn-lièn-pâng khi̍p sṳ̍p-ńg-ke sṳ̀n-yen-koet ke koet-kâ ngièn-sú, thùng-sṳ̀ ya-he Yîn-koet koet-kau ke chui-kô sú-liâng.

George Washington, 1775-ngièn chṳ 1783-ngièn Mî-koet Thu̍k-li̍p Chan-châng sṳ̀ chhṳ̍t-mìn thi-kiûn ke chúng-sṳ̂-lin, 1789-ngièn sṳ̀n-vì Mî-koet thi 1 ngim Chúng-thúng, chhai chiap-lièn lióng-kài sién-kí chûng tû tet-liáu chhiòn-thí sién-kí-thòn mò-yi-ngi kî-chhṳ̀, yit-chhṳ̍t tâm-ngim chúng-thúng chhṳ̍t-to 1797-ngièn.
Woodrow Wilson，, Mî-koet thi ngi-sṳ̍p-pat ngim chúng-thúng.
Franklin Delano Roosevelt
John Fitzgerald Kennedy，, Mî-koet thi sâm-sṳ̍p-ńg ngim chúng-thúng, ngim-khì chhiùng 1961-ngièn 1-ngie̍t 20-ngit khôi-sṳ́ chhṳ̍t-to 1963-ngièn 11-ngie̍t 22-ngit.
Gerald Rudolph Ford, Jr.
James Earl Carter, Jr, 1924-ngièn 10-ngie̍t 1-ngit – ), he Mî-koet ke thi 39-ngim Chúng-thúng.
Thomas Jefferson, Mî-li Kiên-Ha̍p Chung-koet thi-sâm ngim Chúng-thúng.
Ronald Wilson Reagan，, Mî-koet yu-yi̍t chṳn-chhṳ-kâ, thi sâm-sṳ̍p-sâm ngim Kâ-li-fuk-nì-â-chû chû-chóng, thi si-sṳ̍p ngim Mî-koet chúng-thúng.
William Jefferson Clinton, nit chhṳ̂n Bill Clinton, Mî-koet Li̍t-sṳ̂, Chṳn-chhṳ-kâ, Mìn-chú-tóng sṳ̀n-yèn, chên chhòng-khì tâm-ngim Arkansas Chû-chhòng fò thi 42 ngim Mî-koet Chúng-thúng.
Augustus, ngièn-miàng Gaius Octavius Thurinus, he Lò-mâ Ti-koet ke khôi-koet kiûn-chú, thúng-chhṳ Lò-mâ chhòng-tha̍t 43-ngièn.
Khiet-sṳ̍t-é he chṳ́ chhai kiê-hong lâu ngìn pûn-fan sṳ̍t ke ngìn.
Sên-lî-ngìn he cho mâi mai ke ngìn.
Pó-lò, he Sṳ̀n só kién-sién, chiong fuk-yîm chhòn-pûn ngoi-pâng-ngìn ke sṳ́-thù, ya-phî Li̍t-sṳ́-ho̍k-kâ kûng-ngin he tui-yî chó-khì Kau-fi fat-chán kung-hien chui-thai ke sṳ́-thù.

Thai-sṳ́, he Yit-koet Ngièn-sú hiong chu chhai koet Ngièn-sú phai khién ke tén-kip chui-kô ke ngoi-kâu thoi-péu, chhai chu chhai koet yû thoi-péu pún koet koet-kâ Ngièn-sú lâu chṳn-fú hiong chu chhai koet péu-tha̍t yi-kien fe̍t-chá thùng chu chhai koet tha̍t sṳ̀n hia̍p-ngi ke chhiòn khièn, hióng yû vàn-chhiòn ke ngoi-kâu thi̍t khièn lâu ngoi-kâu hot miên khièn, khì só hióng lî nyì ya kha khì-thâ ngoi-kâu thoi-péu vì kô.
Yà-ôi, ya cho-tet ham-cho yà-ngiòng fe̍t-chá fu-mû, he tui â-pâ lâu â-mê ke thúng-chhṳ̂n.
Yo̍k-sṳ̂ he fu-chit thì-kiûng yo̍k-vu̍t tî-sṳt khi̍p yo̍k-sṳ fu̍k-vu ke chôn-ngia̍p ngìn-yèn.
Kiám-chhà-kôn he chú-thô hìn-sṳ hí-sṳ ke fap-li̍t kûng-chok-chá.
Ho̍k-sâng he chṳ́ chhai koet-kâ ngin-khó ke ho̍k-káu thu̍k-sû ke ngìn.
Liá-piên "Yî-sên" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"醫生" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Â-pâ ya cho-tet ham-cho yà, he yà-ôi lî-tú nàm ke ke-ke.
Ló-kûng ya cho tet ham cho chhong-fû, he chṳ́ ńg-ngìn ke phi-ngiéu.
Pû-ngiòng he chṳ́ nàm-ngìn ke phi-ngiéu.
Kazakh-chhu̍k he Chûng-Â ke Kazakhstan chú-thí mìn-chhu̍k, ya-he Chûng-koet yit-ke Séu-su mìn-chhu̍k.
Yù-mu̍k mìn-chhu̍k khiùn-thí chhín-hiong chhiùng yit-chhú yì-kî to nang yit-chhú, tô-yî thin-kî yit-thi.
Tatar-chhu̍k he Chûng-Â ke yit ke mìn-chhu̍k.
Mùng-kú-tshu̍k he Tûng-pet-â tsú-yeu mìn-tshu̍k tsṳ̂-yit, ya-he Mùng-kú-koet ke tsú-thí mìn-tshu̍k.
Yâ-fò-fà he Kî-tuk-kau «Khiu-yok Sṳn-kîn» tú ki-chai ke Sông-ti ke miàng-sṳ.
Chêu-sién-chhu̍k he Tûng-Â chú-yeu mìn-chhu̍k chṳ̂-yit.
Alexander Graham Bell Sean Connery Alex Ferguson James Liuk-Sṳ David Livingstone James Watt Ewan Mcgregor Andy Murray Adam Smith Sû-kak-làn-ngìn he Sû-kak-làn tông-thi ke thú-chho̍k mìn-chhu̍k.
Sierra Leone he Fî-chû ke yit-ke koet-kâ.
Chhâm-siòng Hak-kâ-fa Hon-sṳ pán-pún.

Mò-tóng-sit, fe̍t chhṳ̂n Mò-tóng-phai, thu̍k-li̍p ngìn-sṳ, he chṳ́ put su̍k-yî ngim-hò chṳn-tóng ke kûng-chṳt ngìn-yèn fe̍t yû yit-thin yáng-hióng-li̍t ke ngìn, chhai sién-kí sṳ̀ yu chhṳ̂n-vì thu̍k-li̍p Hèu-sién-ngìn, chhai Chûng-koet Thai-liu̍k hêm-cho Mò-tóng-phai Ngìn-sṳ.
Â-kûng he yit-chúng Chhîn-su̍k kôan-he ke chhṳ̂n-fû.
Yù-thai-ngìn, he kóng-fàm fûn-phu yî sṳ-kie kak-koet ke yit-ke chhu̍k-khiùn.
Pok-sṳ he kau-yuk kî-kèu su-yî ke chui-kô yit-kip ho̍k-vi.
Nùng-mìn ya ham cho nùng-kâ-ngìn, he chṳ́ yung nùng-ngia̍p lòi vì-chhṳ̀ sâng-fa̍t ke ngìn.
Kau-sṳ̂ he chôn-mùn kâu-sû ke chṳt-ngia̍p.

Li̍t-sṳ̂ he chṳ́ su tông-sṳ-ngìn ve-thok fe̍t fap-yen chṳ́ -thin, yî fap-li̍t hia̍p-chhu tông-sṳ-ngìn chin-hàng su-siùng, chhut-thìn phien-fu, yî-khi̍p chhú-lî yû-kôan fap-li̍t sṳ-vu ke chôn-ngia̍p ngìn-yèn.
Liá-piên "Yâ-sû" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"耶穌基督" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Fa-ho̍k kâ yit-pân he chṳ́ chhiùng-sṳ yî khiûn hien-thoi Fa-ho̍k ngièn-kiu ke Khô-ho̍k-kâ, yû chôn-chṳ lâu kiâm chṳt chṳ̂ fûn, chhai Yîn-koet yi̍t khó chṳ́ yo̍k-tsì-sṳ̂.
Sâng-vu̍t Ho̍k-kâ fe̍t Sâng-vu̍t Khô-ho̍k-kâ, he vông-vông chhai kì-têu ke fàn-kin poi-kín hâ ngièn-kiu sâng-vu̍t-thí ke Khô-ho̍k-kâ.
Yên-yèn he chṳ́ chôn-chṳt yên-chhut, fe̍t-chá chhai péu-yên ngi-su̍t chûng pàn-yên mêu-chúng kok-set ke ngìn-vu̍t.
Sîn-ngiòng yit-chhṳ̀ yit-pân lòi-kóng he chôn chṳ́ tui-yî khok-li̍p fûn-yîn kôan-he ke nàm-ńg chhai kiet-fûn ngì-sṳt chûng ke ńg-fông ke chhṳ̂n-fû, nàm-fông chet chhṳ̂n Sîn-lòng.
Â-mê ya cho-tet ham-cho ôi, he yà-ôi lî-tú ńg ke ke-ke.
Liá-piên "Thomas Eddison" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"托馬斯·阿爾瓦·愛迪生" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Se-moi-ngìn, ya cho-tet ham-cho moi-é-ngìn fe̍t-chá ńg-ngìn, he tsṳ́-tsṳ́ tshṳ-sin ke Ngìn-lui, lâu Nàm-ngìn, ya tshiu-he hiùng-sin ngìn-lui sṳ̀n-vì tui-pí.
Se-lai-ngìn, ya cho-tet ham-cho nàm-é-ngìn fe̍t-chá nàm-ngìn, he chṳ́ yit-ke hiùng-sin ngìn-lui, lâu tshṳ-sin ngìn-lui, ya tshiu-he Ńg-ngìn sṳ̀n-vì tui-pí.
Fî- yí Mî-koet Het-ngìn tsṳ́-tsak Mî-koet Het-ngìn.
Kôn-liâu ya chhṳ̂n-cho Kôn-yèn.
Vì-kîn-ngìn he Nok-ngì-sṳ̂-ngìn ke yit-kî, kì-têu he chhiùng Kûng-ngièn 8 Sṳ-ki to 11 Sṳ-ki chhîm yéu pin chhṳ̍t-mìn Êu-chû yèn-hói fò Yîn-koet tó-yí ke Thâm-hiám-kâ, vú sṳ, sông-ngìn fò hói tho.
Dwight David Eisenhower, he Mî-koet Liu̍k-kiûn Ńg-sên Sông-chiông lâu thi 34-ngim Chúng-thúng.
Phù-sat hai Fut-kaau yap-pin yit ko san-wai.
Dalai Lama he Sî-chhông fu̍t-kau ke Tulku chṳ̂ yit.
Mô Chhe̍t-tûng, he Chûng-koet Khiung-sán-tóng ke chui-kô liâng-thô-ngìn, kì fat-thung Vùn-fa Thai Kiet-min.
Ló-chṳ́ he Chûng-koet chhûn-chhiû sṳ̀-thoi sṳ̂-sióng-kâ,chat-ho̍k-kâ.Kì he tho-kâ ho̍k-sot ke thoi-péu ngìn-vu̍t,yû tho-tet-kîn 5000 sṳ chhòn-sṳ.Kì hàn phî tho-kau fung-vi sṳ́-chú.
Julius Caesar, Lò-mâ Khiung-fò-koet ma̍t-khì ke kiûn-sṳ thúng-soi, chṳn-chhṳ-kâ, Yî-lio̍k kâ-chhu̍k sṳ̀n-yèn.
John Maynard Keynes, Yîn-koet Kîn-chi ho̍k-kâ.
Isaac Newton khì-sṳ, yîn-koet vu̍t-lí-ho̍k-kâ, sṳ-ho̍k-kâ, thiên-vùn-ho̍k-kâ, chhṳ-yèn chet-ho̍k-kâ.
Sṳt-kâ-mèu-nì he fu̍t-kau ke chhong-sṳ́-ngìn, sàng-fu̍t heu chhṳ̂n-cho fu̍t-thò, mìn-kiên chhṳ̂n kì cho fu̍t-chú, yi-sii he chha̍t-ngu yî-chhiu ngìn-sên chá.
Karl Marx, Hon-sṳ yîm-yi̍t Mâ-khiet-sṳ̂, he Tet-koet ke yi-chak chhut-miàng ke chet-ho̍k-kâ lâu sa-fi-ho̍k-kâ.
Mâ-tên Lu-tet chó-chhôi Ngí-fut-thai-ho̍k thu̍k vùn-ho̍k, yu-yû ho̍k pan-ngièn Fap-li̍t.
Homeros he Kú Hî-lia̍p ke yit ke sṳ̂-ngìn.
Genghis Khan ，he Mùng-kú Ti-koet thien-kî-chá、sṳ-kie li̍t-sṳ́ sông khiet-chhut ke Kiûn-sṳ thúng-soi.
Liá-piên "Albert Einstein" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"阿爾伯特·愛因斯坦" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.

Dmitri Ivanovich Mendeleev (Ngò-ngî: Дми́трий Ива́нович Менделе́ев) 1834-ngièn ngi-ngie̍t tshit-ngit － 1907-ngièn ngi-ngie̍t ngi-ngit), Sṳ̍p-kiú Sṳ-ki Ngò-koet Khô-ho̍k-kâ, fat-hien Fa-ho̍k ngièn-su ke tsû-khì sin, tseu-tén ngièn-tsṳ́ liong, tsṳ-tsho tshut-lòi sṳ-kie song thi-yit tsông Ngièn-su Tsû-khì-péu.
Vladimir Lenin, Hon-sṳ yîm-yi̍t Lie̍t-nèn, ngièn-lòi miàng-sṳ hêm cho Vladimir Ilyich Ulyanov, he Ngò-lò-sṳ̂ lâu Sû-lièn ke yi-chak chṳn-chhṳ-kâ.
Joseph Vissarionovich Stalin, ngièn-lòi miàng-sṳ hêm cho Ioseb Besarionis dze Jughashvili, he Sû-lièn ke yi-chak chṳn-chhṳ-kâ.
Chhòn-kau-sṳ he chṳ́ kiên-thin ke sin chhṳ-kâ ke chûng-kau, hàng-to chṳ̂n yén ke thi-khî hiong phe̍t-sà siên-chhòn chhṳ-kâ chûng-kau ke ngìn.
Chhù-sṳ̂ he chôn-mùn pûn ngìn chú-sṳ̍t ke chṳt-ngia̍p.
Kau-su he yit-chúng kô-tén kau-yuk thí-ne chûng ke chṳt-chhṳ̂n.
Kiûn-ngìn he yit chúng chhai koet-kâ kiûn-chhui fuk-yi̍t ke chṳt-ngia̍p.

Chúng-thúng he tui Khiung-fò chṳ koet-kâ Ngièn-sú ke chhṳ̂n-fû Chúng-thúng ke Yîn-vùn yi̍t chhṳ̂n "President", chhai Yîn-vùn chûng he chṳ́ liâng-thô chá, chhai Lò-mâ Ti-koet sṳ̀-khì vì fu chṳp-chṳn kôn fe̍t hàng sén chúng tuk ke chṳt vi, pin fî chṳp-chṳn kôn.
Neil Armstrong, Mî-koet Thai-khûng-ngìn, Chhṳ-fî-yèn, Hói-kiûn Fî-hàng-yèn yî-khi̍p Thai-ho̍k Kau-su.
Sṳ-chhòng, he khiûn-thoi yit-ke sàng-sṳ chui-kô chṳt-vi kôn-yèn ke chṳt chhṳ̂n.
Sîm-khiû ya cho-tet ham-cho sîm-khiû-é, he lai-é ke pû-ngiòng.
Chhâm-siòng Hak-kâ-ngî Pha̍k-fa-sṳ pán-pún.

Mî-li-kiên Ha̍p-chung-koet Chúng-thúng he Mî-koet ke Koet-kâ Ngièn-sú, Chṳn-fú Sú-nó lâu Sâm-kiûn Thúng-soi, kîn-kí 1787-ngièn thûng-ko ke Mî-koet Hièn-fap yì sat-li̍p, hàng sṳ́ Hièn-fap fù yi ke hàng-chṳn-khièn, sú ngim Chúng-thúng George Washington yî 1789-ngièn 4-ngie̍t 30-ngit chhiu chṳt, chṳ̂-heu chṳ 1933 ke li̍t ngim Chúng-thúng kiûn vì 3-ngie̍t 4-ngit chhiu chṳt, yì khì heu chet yî 1-ngie̍t 20-ngit chhiu chṳt.
Song-ti tu mò khiung-yong ke chûng-kau tî-tú yû mò khiung-yong ke yi-sṳ.
Sîm-khiû ya cho-tet ham-cho sîm-khiû-é, he lai-é ke pû-ngiòng.
George H. W. Bush he Mî-koet thi si-sṳ̍p-yit ngim Chúng-thúng.
Friedrich Engels, Hon-sṳ yîm-yi̍t Ên-kak-sṳ̂, he Tet-koet ke yi-chak chhut-miàng ke chet-ho̍k-kâ, li̍t-sṳ́-ho̍k-kâ lâu sông-ngìn.
Chhṳ̍t-sien, he yit-ke tiám chhai phìn-mien fe̍t khûng-kiên yèn chho̍k yit-thin fông-hiong lâu khì siông-fán fông-hiong yun-thûng ke kuí-chiak. mò-vân-khiuk ke sièn.
Chhṳ̍t-sien, he yit-ke tiám chhai phìn-mien fe̍t khûng-kiên yèn chho̍k yit-thin fông-hiong lâu khì siông-fán fông-hiong yun-thûng ke kuí-chiak. mò-vân-khiuk ke sièn.
Liá-piên "Sṳ̂-chhù-chṳ̂-lu" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"絲綢之路" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Sân he yit-chúng pûn phiàng-thi pâu-vì ke, kô-thu pí chû-vì kô ke thin-hìn.
Alpes sân he yit-chho vi-yî Êu-chû chûng-sîm ke Sân-mak, kì fu̍k-koi liáu Yi-thai-li pet-phu piên-kie, Fap-koet tûng-nàm-phu, Sui-sṳ, Liechtenstein, O-thi-li, Tet-koet nàm-phu khi̍p Slovenia.
Gibraltar he 14-ke Yîn-koet Hói-ngoi liâng-thú chṳ̂ yit, ya-he chui-séu ke yit-ke, vi yî Iberia Pan-tó ke ma̍t-tôn, he thûng-vông Thi-chûng-hói ke ngi̍p-khiéu.
Chomolangma Fûng he chhai-yî Chûng-koet lâu Nepal kâu-kie ke Himalaya Sân-mak chṳ̂-song, chûng-ngièn chit-siet. he sṳ-kie hói-pha̍t thi-yit kô-fûng.
Himalaya Sân-mak he sṳ-kie hói-pha̍t chui-kô ke Sân-mak, vi-yî Â-chû ke Chûng-koet Sî-chhòng Chhṳ-chhṳ-khî lâu Pakistan, Yin-thu, Nepal, Bhtan tén koet piên kin sông.
Vû-là-ngì Sân-mak he Ngò-lò-sṳ̂ kin-nui thai-yok nàm-pet chéu hiong ke yit-chho Sân-mak, kì vi-yî Ngò-lò-sṳ̂ ke chûng sî-phu.

Fu-sṳ-sân he Ngit-pún yit-chho vàng-khiam Chhin-kông-yen lâu Sân-lî-yen ke fa̍t-fó-sân, vi yî Tûng-kîn sî-nàm-fông yok 80 kûng-lî, chú-fûng hói-pha̍t 3776 kûng-chhak, 2002-ngièn 8-ngie̍t, kîn Ngit-pún Koet-thú Thi-lî-yen chhùng-sîn chhet-liòng heu, vì 3775.63 kûng-chhak, he Ngit-pún koet-nui ke chui-kô fûng.

Rocky Sân-mak, he Pet-mî-chû sî-phu ke chú-yeu sân-mak, chhiùng Kâ-nâ-thai sî-phu British Columbia vàng-ye̍t Mî-koet sî-phu, chhṳ̍t to Mî-koet sî-nàm-phu ke Sîn Me̍t-sî-kô-chû, mièn-yèn chhêu-ko 4,800 kûng-lî.
Kit-li̍t-mâ-chap-lò Sân vi-yî Thán-sông-nì-â tûng-pet ke Kit-li̍t-mâ-chap-lò-khî, lìm khiûn Khén-nì-â piên-kie, sṳ-fî chû ke chui-kô sân, sòng pûn chhṳ̂n-vì “ Fî-chû vuk tsit ”, “ Fî-chû chṳ̂ vòng ”.
Liá-piên "Khô-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"科學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Su-ho̍k, he ngièn-kiu su-liòng, kiet-kièu, khûng-kiên, kîn pien-fa ke it-mùn ho̍k-khô.
Thi-khiù Khô-ho̍k he chṳ́ yit-chhiet ngièn-kiu Thi-khiù ke Khô-ho̍k, he Hàng-sên Khô-ho̍k ke chôn-mùn fûn-kî.
Euclid Kí-hò chṳ́ on-cheu Euclid ke 《Kí-hò ngièn-pún》 kèu-chho ke Kí-hò-ho̍k.
Thi-lî-ho̍k he kôan-yî thi-khiù khi̍p khì thi̍t-chṳ̂n, kî-mìn lâu hien-siong ke ho̍k-mun.
Liù-thí li̍t-ho̍k he li̍t-ho̍k ke yit-mùn kî, ngiên-kiu li̍t-ho̍k hien-siong lèu li̍t-ho̍k hàng-vì ke Khô-ho̍k.
Liá-piên "Kháu-kú-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"考古學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Sâng-thai-ho̍k, he Tet-koet Sâng-vu̍t ho̍k-kâ Ernst Haeckel yî 1866-ngièn thin-ngi ke yit-ke khói-ngiam: sâng-thai-ho̍k he ngièn-kiu sâng-vu̍t-thí lâu khì chû-vì fàn-kin siông-fu kôan-he ke Khô-ho̍k.
Thien-nó Khô-ho̍k he hì-thúng-sin ngièn-kiu chṳ̂-sín lâu kie-son ke lî-lun kî-chhú yî-khi̍p kì-têu chhai thien-nó hì-thúng chûng yì-hò sṳ̍t-hien lâu yin-yung ke sṳ̍t-yung kî-su̍t ke ho̍k-khô.
Kî-hài Kûng-chhàng he li-yung vu̍t-lî thin-li̍t vì kî-hài ne-thúng tsok fûn-sak, sat-kie, sên-sán khi̍p vì-siû ke kûng-chhàng ho̍k-khô.
Mì-chit-fûn-ho̍k he ngièn-kiu Khi̍t-han, Mì-fûn-ho̍k, Chit-fûn-ho̍k lâu Mò-khiùng-kip-sú ke yit-ke Sú-ho̍k fûn-kî, pin sṳ̀n-vì-liáu hien-thoi Thai-ho̍k kau-yuk ke chhùng-yeu chû-sṳ̀n phu-fûn.
Liá-piên "Thiên-vùn-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"天文學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Liá-piên "Kîn-chi-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"經濟學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Liá-piên "Fa-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"化學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Liá-piên "Kûng-chhàng-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"工程學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Mì-fûn chhai Sú-ho̍k chûng he tui hâm-sú ke khiu̍k-phu pien-fa-sut ke yit-chúng "sien-sin mèu-shu̍t".
Kí-hò-ho̍k, kién-chhṳ̂n Kí-hò he Sú-ho̍k ke yit-ke kî-chhú fûn-kî, chú-yeu ngièn-kiu khûng-kiên khî-vet kôan-he yî-khi̍p khûng-kiên hìn-sṳt ke thu-liòng.
Liá-piên "Chet-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"哲學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Liá-piên "Vu̍t-lî-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"物理學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Sîm-lî-ho̍k he yit-mùn ngièn-kiu ngìn-lui khi̍p thûng-vu̍t ke sîm-lî hien-siong, chîn-sṳ̀n kûng-nèn lâu hàng-vì ke Khô-ho̍k, ki he yit-mùn lî-lun ho̍k-khô, ya-he yit-mùn yin-yung ho̍k-khô.
Liá-piên "Sâng-vu̍t-ho̍k" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"生物學" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Chhṳ-yèn Khô-ho̍k he ngièn-kiu thai chhṳ-yèn chûng yû-kî fe̍t mò-kî ke sṳ-vu̍t lâu hien-siong ke Khô-ho̍k.
Ngìn-lui-ho̍k he ngièn-kiu ngìn ke ho̍k-khô.
Hon-ho̍k fe̍t chhṳ̂n Chûng-koet-ho̍k he chṳ́ Chûng-koet yî-ngoi ke Ho̍k-chá tui yû-kôan Chûng-koet ke-fông fông-mien chin-hàng ngièn-kiu ke yit-mùn ho̍k-khô.
Liá-piên "Thùng" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"銅" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Chṳ̂-pún chú-ngi he yit-chúng Kîn-chi-ho̍k ke chṳ-thu, tì liá-yong ke chṳ-thu ha, sông-ngia̍p sán-phín lâu fu̍k-vu chia-chho̍k fo-pi chhai chhṳ-yù sṳ-chhòng liù-thung.
Kám-fap he yit chúng kî-pún son-su̍t yun-son, fù-ho he „-“, kiet-kó ham cho „chhâ“.
Sṳ̀n-fap he yit chúng son-su̍t yun-son, fù-ho he „×“, kiet-kó ham cho „chit“.
Chhù-fap he yit chúng son-su̍t yun-son, fù-ho he „÷“, kiet-kó ham cho „sông“.
Kâ-fap he yit chúng kî-pún son-su̍t yun-son, fù-ho he „+“, kiet-kó ham cho „fò“.
Thai-nàm-sà he yit-chúng mò kiok ke phà-hàng thung-vu̍t.
Meu-khô pâu-koat sṳ̂-é, lo-fú lâu pau-é tén thung-vu̍t, he sṳ̍t-ngiuk-muk ke kiú-ke khô-chûng chui vi ngiuk-sṳ̍t-sin ke Phú-nen thung-vu̍t.
Vòng-cha̍t, fe̍t-chá ham-cho ki-cha̍t, he yit-chúng chhùng-è.
Làn-fâ he yit-chúng fâ.
Thông-phûng he yit-chúng fî-hàng ke khiùn-kî khûn-chhùng, su̍k-yî Phûng-chhu̍k, chhái-sṳ̍t fâ-fún lâu fâ-me̍t pin yòng-chho phûng-me̍t.
Fôn-hìn-muk chhai tiâu-lui chhòn-thúng fûn-lui ne-thúng chûng he tiâu-kong chûng ke yit-ke muk.

Chhú-khô (Ho̍k-miàng: Muridae), Phú-nen-kong Ngat-chhṳ́-muk ke yit khô, pâu-koat kâ-chhú, lî-chhú, thièn-chhú, chhó-ngièn thu-mî-chhú) tén chṳ̂ hí-tô sòng-kien thûng-vu̍t, ngièn-sán yî Â-chû, Êu-chû, Fî-chû, Àu-chû tén kóng-thai thi-khî, hien-chhai chet yí phiên-pu Thi-khiù mî-ke kok-lo̍k.
Thòn-ǹg he yit-chúng phà-hàng thung-vu̍t.
Kâm-cha he Vò-pún-khô ke Tân-chṳ́-ya̍p Chhṳ̍t-vu̍t, vi Kâm-cha-su̍k ke chúng-chhṳ̂n.
Pân-kiêu-é, chhai thung-vu̍t fûn-lui ho̍k sông he Pân-kiêu-khô ke yit-ke su̍k.
Liá-piên "Ngo̍k-ǹg" ke ya̍p-mien he pha̍k-fa-sṳ, yû hon-sṳ lièn-kiet"鱷魚" ke ya̍p-mien chhai liá-hong tiám-chhut.
Vû-yìn vi Sûng-yi̍t-muk tón-kok â-muk khûn-chhùng chṳ̂-yit, chhiòn sṳ-kie yok-yû sâm-chhiên chúng.

Pak-ha̍p-fâ ya cho-tet ham cho pa-hà-fâ fe̍t-chá tá-vón-fâ, he yit-tsúng tshṳ̍t-vu̍t, ngièn-sán tshai-yî Chûng-koet, tsú-yeu fûn-phu tì Â-chû tûng-phu, Eû-chû、Pet-mî-chû tén-tén Pet-pan-khiù vûn-tai thi-khî, tshiòn-khiù yí-kîn fat-hien yû yit-pak tô-ke phín-tsúng, khì-tsûng ńg-sṳ̍p-ńg tsûng sán-yî Chûng-koet.
Ló-â-é, ya cho-tet ham-cho vû-â, he chṳ̂n-tô sàng-sṳ fî-sòng kien-tó ke tiâu-é.
Lièn-lî he yit-chúng thung-vu̍t.
7-ngie̍t 1-ngit he Gregorius La̍k-fap ngièn tî-tú ke thi 182 ngit, lì ngièn-mî hàn-yû 183 ngit.
Yîm-fù sṳ̀-chhṳ̍t, chhai ngo̍k-phú chûng yung-lòi péu-tha̍t kok yîm-fù chṳ̂-kiên ke siông-tui chhṳ̀-sa sṳ̀-kiên.

Tsui-heu ke Sṳ́m-phan fe̍t-tsá tshṳ̂n-tso Thai Sṳ́m-phan he yit-tsúng tsûng-kau sṳ̂-sióng, tshai sṳ-kie ma̍t-ngit tsṳ-̂sṳ̀ Sṳ̀n voi tshut-hien, tsiông sí-tsá fu̍k-sâng pin tsin-hàng tshài-kiet, fûn-khôi yún-sên-tsá lâu tá-ngi̍p thi-ngiu̍k-tsá.

Lî-pai-yit, yú hêm-cho pai-yit, sên-khì-yit lâu ngie̍t-yeu-ngit, he yit-chiak sên-khì tú ke yit thiên, chhai lî-pai-ngit ke heu-mî, lî-pai-ngi ke thèu-chhièn.
Lî-pai-liuk, yú hêm-cho pai-liuk, sên-khì-liuk lâu thú-yeu-ngit, he yit-chiak sên-khì tú ke yit thiên, chhai lî-pai-ńg ke heu-mî, lî-pai-ngit ke thèu-chhièn.
